# Privacy Policy (pursuant to Art. 13 GDPR)

_Last updated: July 2025_

## 1. General Information

We take the protection of your personal data very seriously. We process your data exclusively in accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and the German Federal Data Protection Act (BDSG).

## 2. Controller

The party responsible for data processing under the GDPR is:

**Jelena Foss**  
Email: [info.ioffline@gmail.com](mailto:info.ioffline@gmail.com)

## 3. Data Processing Within the App

### a) Local Data Storage Only

The app processes and stores data exclusively on your device, such as offline time logs, selected settings, and preferences.

### b) No Transmission of Personal Data

No personal data is sent to us or third parties. The app uses no cloud storage, no analytics, and no internet connection.

### c) No User Profiling

We do not create any user profiles or track any personal behavior.

## 4. Legal Basis

The legal basis for local data processing is **Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR** â€“ to provide the app functionality. No data is transmitted to us.

## 5. Your Rights

As no personal data is stored by us, rights like access, correction, or deletion apply only to the data stored on your own device.

## 6. No Data Transfers

No data is transferred to third countries or external services.

## 7. Voluntary Use

You are not required to provide any personal data. The app can be used without entering identifiable information.

